{"ja386:0.1":"Jataka ","ja386:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","ja386:0.3":"Kharaputtavagga ","ja386:0.4":"1. Kharaputtajataka ","ja386:1.1":"“Saccam kirevamahamsu, ","ja386:1.2":"vastam baloti pandita; ","ja386:1.3":"Passa balo rahokammam, ","ja386:1.4":"avikubbam na bujjhati”. ","ja386:2.1":"“Tvam khopi samma balosi, ","ja386:2.2":"kharaputta vijanahi; ","ja386:2.3":"Rajjuya hi parikkhitto, ","ja386:2.4":"vankottho ohitomukho. ","ja386:3.1":"Aparampi samma te balyam, ","ja386:3.2":"yo mutto na palayasi; ","ja386:3.3":"So ca balataro samma, ","ja386:3.4":"yam tvam vahasi senakam”. ","ja386:4.1":"“Yannu samma aham balo, ","ja386:4.2":"ajaraja vijanahi; ","ja386:4.3":"Atha kena senako balo, ","ja386:4.4":"tam me akkhahi pucchito”. ","ja386:5.1":"“Uttamattham labhitvana, ","ja386:5.2":"bhariyaya yo padassati; ","ja386:5.3":"Tena jahissatattanam, ","ja386:5.4":"sa cevassa na hessati”. ","ja386:6.1":"“Na ve piyammeti janinda tadiso, ","ja386:6.2":"Attam nirankatva piyani sevati; ","ja386:6.3":"Attava seyyo parama ca seyyo, ","ja386:6.4":"Labbha piya ocitatthena paccha”ti. ","ja386:7.1":"Kharaputtajatakam pathamam. "}